Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.94,0:04:36.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.82,0:05:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.73,0:05:23.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:30.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:39.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.60,0:05:55.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.31,0:05:58.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.10,0:05:59.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.11,0:06:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:16.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.93,0:06:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一堂是自習課 太幸運了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.60,0:06:37.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然召開教師會議 真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.52,0:06:40.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說那件事是真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:42.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.82,0:06:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是高三學長自殺的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.32,0:06:49.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.41,0:06:55.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不只是我們學校 據說前陣子也有人從屋頂跳樓
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.33,0:06:57.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 剛剛在說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.01,0:07:13.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音應該不會知道那些事的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.60,0:07:14.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.81,0:07:17.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也只是聽說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.90,0:07:22.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡聽到的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.31,0:07:25.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在網上
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.82,0:07:29.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經熟悉那電腦了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.20,0:07:31.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一次試給我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊 不過計算機稍微改裝過了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.91,0:07:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,改裝？ 玲音竟然會對那種東西有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.00,0:07:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最近好像變了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.42,0:07:47.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.71,0:07:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.63,0:07:52.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.93,0:07:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網上的人怎麼說？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像跟電腦遊戲有關
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.23,0:08:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲？ 網絡遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.23,0:08:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不太清楚 沒玩過
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.11,0:08:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但聽說死去的人全部都是沉迷這個遊戲的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.62,0:08:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男生最愛這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.33,0:08:20.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遊戲啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.50,0:08:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到底是為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.50,0:08:23.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:28.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用吃的這麼急 小心點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.80,0:08:30.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.30,0:08:33.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想先走了 行嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.80,0:08:36.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用什麼事都問我們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼急事？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想回家裝好電腦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:42.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒有把它裝好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.44,0:08:45.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,電腦比朋友重要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.90,0:08:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茱莉不要為難她
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.23,0:08:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.40,0:08:53.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 裝好後別忘了讓我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.24,0:08:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.03,0:09:00.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音真的改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 來 給你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:20.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是我不對
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.70,0:09:41.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Login 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.54,0:09:43.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程序執行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:54.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Voice mail
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好嗎？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我的問題 我一個人我無法解決
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.31,0:10:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請教了研究室的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你真的想要用Psyche
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.61,0:10:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要電腦的超頻率提高配合才可以使用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.82,0:10:20.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然電腦的規格大致一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:23.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是有一些使用上的差別
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:25.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你成功 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.00,0:10:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有問題再跟我聯繫 再見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.02,0:10:49.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,JJ
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.23,0:10:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干麻？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.31,0:10:53.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近學生流行哪種網上遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.73,0:10:56.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是「幻影」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:01.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了吧 那不是像你這種大人玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？ 玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人的吧 是真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道我的耳朵聽錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.53,0:11:49.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經不玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一點關係也沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是網路的世界 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.73,0:12:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.02,0:12:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 不要逃
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.53,0:13:06.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是玩遊戲的人嗎？ 救救我！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.00,0:13:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.50,0:13:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.81,0:13:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束槍發射
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.41,0:13:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.71,0:13:58.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:13:59.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.80,0:14:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.64,0:14:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:26.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是覺得很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.63,0:15:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒發現她是一個小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.13,0:15:33.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那完全不是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我完全不知情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.31,0:15:47.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻影是需要利用專用加速程序配合 用了那個才能玩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.23,0:15:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之前從一個非法服務器下載了那個程序
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.70,0:16:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個遊戲對我們來說只是個動作遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:04.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是一個能刺激我們感官的連線對戰遊戲廳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.92,0:16:06.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼兒園中兒童用的電腦為什麼能連上線？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您有一封E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.31,0:16:19.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開它
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.02,0:16:24.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 想不到你竟然對幻影產生興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.32,0:16:29.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概查了一下怎麼也搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.70,0:16:35.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是什麼特殊的網絡遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.82,0:16:38.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是能修改遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.04,0:16:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問題是出在修改的部份
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.12,0:16:46.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,程序似乎有地方怪怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:51.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想這該不會是KNIGHTS所做的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KNIGHTS？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.73,0:17:02.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.44,0:17:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經很熟練了 網絡世界的往來方式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.24,0:17:14.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我給你個輔助性的建議
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.20,0:17:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.32,0:17:15.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.91,0:17:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,網絡是用來傳達訊息
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.70,0:17:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一個方便溝通聯絡的空間
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:26.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能與現實世界混淆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.71,0:17:34.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能瞭解我所講的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.30,0:17:39.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個世界根本沒有分別
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.23,0:17:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就能完全控制它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.32,0:18:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我便能進入完全區域和完全動態
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.70,0:18:05.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使新型的電腦也做不到這樣的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.42,0:18:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的 我改造過了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你使用了Phyche？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.51,0:18:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用擔心 因為玲音還是玲音
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.30,0:18:21.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都在這裡等你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.92,0:18:55.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼到現在還不來？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.43,0:19:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會詛咒你…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.52,0:19:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是一則幸運E-MAIL
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.90,0:19:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看過之後便能得到轉機
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.11,0:19:23.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據調查KNIGHTS集團可能根本不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.70,0:19:27.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在網上留言形成的虛擬狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.12,0:19:31.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至可說成是網絡的宗教思想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能跟我約會嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.71,0:19:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若你有男朋友 那就甩了他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你有很愛你的人我才會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.72,0:19:52.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,J9465488 AA97464 「電腦程序」
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.60,0:19:55.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼人都行 若無事 請開啟這封電子郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.61,0:19:59.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請救救我 或許你不相信…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.03,0:20:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我真的一直被人監視著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.33,0:20:12.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玲音 為什麼你還不快來？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.72,0:21:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.73,0:21:17.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我滾
